    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for the CFD hemolysis model applied to the CPB COU is accepted at MRL 2. All seven assessed factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels. The six remaining factors are appropriately scoped out or not assessed per the MRL 2 assessment plan. The model is judged credible for its intended use of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device, supporting the regulatory submission with the relative hemolysis index acceptance criterion (RH < 1) satisfied across all five evaluated operating conditions.",
